  "remarks": "\nANSELM OSKAR SCHMUCKI is an involved person within the meaning of the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 as he is or has been involved in obtaining a benefit from or supporting the Government of Russia by carrying on business in a sector of strategic significance, namely the Russian Financial Services Sector.\n",
